/*Finds the number of days between:
  1 day before the month-to-date start date ([~ mtdStart (Day)] - 1)
  & a future date obtained by adding the number of days 
    ([ . spendCheck (numDays)]) to today's date.
Then subtracts 1 from the final result.
*/
DATEDIFF('day', [~ mtdStart (Day)] - 1, DATEADD('day', [. spendCheck (numDays)], TODAY())) - 1
